<metal:master use-macro="master">

  <metal:title fill-slot="title">Invalid Configuration!</metal:title>

  <metal:body fill-slot="body">

  <h2>Invalid Configuration</h2>
  <p>We were unable to communicate with the Twitter server. This is probably
  because the administrator of this app has not set up the Twitter OAuth settings
  correctly.</p>
  
    <p><a href="/admin" tal:condition="admin">Click here</a> to set the OAuth settings.</p>

    <p tal:condition="not admin">Ask your administrator to set up the OAuth settings on the admin page.</p>

  </metal:body>
</metal:master>